  "text": "Primary outcomes were re-test attendance, and re-test attendance within recommended timeframe, both recorded as dichotomous variables. Re-test was considered within the recommended time frame when was performed between month 12 and 18 after primary screening [CITATION_1] . Women who returned up to 30 days off the range were also included.",
